name: 2nd International Conference on Public Health and Well-being 2020
content: 2nd International Conference on Public health and Well-being 2020 will be gathering the foremost academicians, clinicians, public health professionals, health workers, policy makers and other related professionals who will be presenting their researches, innovative projects and best practices which will lead to significant discoveries and a remarkable improvement in public health and well-being. The conference will be organized by iConferences and we welcome Public health professionals from every part of the world to be engaged in this networking platform to be held on 25th â€“ 26th June 2020 in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.
